# Development

## Run test

Prerequisite: tox and python 3.7, 3.8, 3.9, 3.10

If you are using pyenv virtualenv, you might need to install all python versions and run `pyenv local 3.7.x 3.8.x 3.9.x 3.10.x` at the first time.

```bash
cd lti1p3platform
tox
```
